videos.headline: Geno Auriemma becomes winningest coach in college basketball history
videos.description: UConn's Geno Auriemma earns the 1,217th win of his career, passing Tara VanDerveer for the most coaching victories in NCAA basketball history.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Geno Auriemma becomes winningest coach in college basketball history) 2024/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Geno Auriemma surprised by live goat after historic win
videos.description: UConn women's coach Geno Auriemma is presented a live goat after setting the record for most wins in NCAA basketball history.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Must-See (Geno Auriemma surprised by live goat after historic win) 2024/11/20

videos.headline: Geno hilariously asks fans to storm court during ceremony
videos.description: After setting the all-time wins record, UConn coach Geno Auriemma encourages a group of fans to run onto the court.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Must-See (Geno hilariously asks fans to storm court during ceremony) 2024/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sarah Strong steals and scores for UConn
videos.description: UConn freshman Sarah Strong takes the ball away from Fairleigh Dickinson's Abby Conklin and takes it all the way to score.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Sarah Strong steals and scores for UConn) 2024/11/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Paige Bueckers dishes to Morgan Cheli for a UConn and-1
videos.description: Paige Bueckers sends a pass inside to UConn freshman Morgan Cheli for the hoop and the harm.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Paige Bueckers dishes to Morgan Cheli for a UConn and-1) 2024/11/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kaitlyn Chen plays passing lane for a steal
videos.description: Kaitlyn Chen scores for UConn after making a heads-up play for a steal.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Kaitlyn Chen plays passing lane for a steal) 2024/11/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Paige Bueckers hangs in air for tough and-1
videos.description: Paige Bueckers scores for UConn despite getting fouled while in the air.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Paige Bueckers hangs in air for tough and-1) 2024/11/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sarah Strong feeds Paige Bueckers for basket inside
videos.description: Sarah Strong finds a cutting Paige Bueckers for a bucket against Fairleigh Dickinson.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Sarah Strong feeds Paige Bueckers for basket inside) 2024/11/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sarah Strong splashes triple to match career-high 17 points
videos.description: UConn freshman Sarah Strong continues to feel it vs. Fairleigh Dickinson with her third 3-pointer of the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Sarah Strong splashes triple to match career-high 17 points) 2024/11/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Azzi Fudd's pickpocket steal sets up her first basket of season
videos.description: In her return from injury, Azzi Fudd steals and scores for UConn to close the third quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Azzi Fudd's pickpocket steal sets up her first basket of season) 2024/11/21 ESHEET

videos.headline: Geno Auriemma tells SVP how he has the same fire 40 years later
videos.description: UConn coach Geno Auriemma talks to Scott Van Pelt about how he keeps his competitive fire alive after all of his accomplishments.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Interview (Geno Auriemma tells SVP how he has the same fire 40 years later) 2024/11/20 SVP
